choices.text:
### Human:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today presuming no dietary restrictions.
### Assistant:

Here is your healthy meal plan for the day:
Breakfast: 1 cup of oatmeal with 2 tablespoons of almond butter, 1/4 cup of blueberries and a glass of orange juice.
Lunch: 3 ounces of grilled chicken breast, 1 cup of brown rice, 1 cup of steamed broccoli and a side salad with vinaigrette dressing.
Snack: 1/2 cup of plain Greek yogurt with 1/4 cup of chopped walnuts.
Dinner: 3 ounces of grilled salmon, 1 cup of roasted sweet potatoes and a side salad with vinaigrette dressing.
